@host = http://localhost:3978

### Health check
GET {{host}}/

###

### Get all tickets (empty at start)
GET {{host}}/api/tickets
Accept: application/json

###

### Create a ticket manually (bypasses the bot conversation)
POST {{host}}/api/tickets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Cannot access SharePoint",
  "priority": "High",
  "affectedSystem": "SharePoint",
  "reportedBy": "Ejaz Hussain"
}

###

### Get a specific ticket (replace INC-1001 with the ID returned above)
GET {{host}}/api/tickets/INC-1001
Accept: application/json

###

### Update ticket status
PATCH {{host}}/api/tickets/INC-1001/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "Resolved"
}

###
